OL,3,CWhat's behind the Budget tradition of
OL,4,Cthe chancellor's red box?
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, the Labour government
OL,7,Fwill unveil its second Budget,
OL,8,Foutlining the state of the economy and
OL,9,Fexplaining how it plans to spend and
OL,10,Fraise money across the coming year.
OL,12,FChancellor Rachel Reeves will deliver
OL,13,Fthe annual Budget statement, a speech
OL,14,Fmade to MPs in the House of Commons,
OL,15,Fwhich sets out the government's
OL,16,Fapproach to taxation and spending.
