OL,3,CWhat's behind the Budget tradition of
OL,4,Cthe chancellor's red box?
OL,6,FAhead of her speech, she has been
OL,7,Fphotographed on the steps of 11
OL,8,FDowning Street, holding a red box. But
OL,9,Fwhere did this tradition come from,
OL,10,Fand what is inside?
OL,12,FWhat is the Budget box?
OL,14,FThe chancellor uses the distinctive
OL,15,Fred box to carry the Budget speech
OL,16,Ffrom their official residence in 11
OL,17,FDowning Street to the House of Commons.
OL,19,FEvery year, they pose on the steps of
OL,20,F11 Downing Street while photographs
OL,21,Fare taken of them holding the red box.
