OL,8,FITV News. Direct to your inbox every
OL,9,FFriday morning.
OL,11,FWhy does the chancellor carry it?
OL,13,FThe word Budget originates from the
OL,14,Fold French word for little bag, or
OL,15,F"bougette". The Budget statement has
OL,16,Fhistorically been brought to the
OL,17,FCommons in a leather bag, which has
OL,18,Fsince been replaced by the red box.
